    {
      "content": "Alternative authentication methods",
      "pos": [
        10977,
        11011
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If the gateway authentication services don't meet the needs of your app, you can handle authentication yourself, or use the Azure API Management service.",
      "pos": [
