      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        11761,
        11972
      ],
      "content": "At present App Service does not support using a do-it-yourself solution alongside gateway authentication, as is possible in <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Mobile Services<ept id=\"p1\">](mobile-services-dotnet-backend-get-started-custom-authentication.md)</ept>."
